DTEND:20260809T200000
DESCRIPTION:This 2-day course will teach you the very fundamentals of turni
 ng and proper tool use.  With expert guidance\, you will learn how to safe
 ly and proficiently use a lathe while turning a variety of projects. Tool 
 sharpening\, materials selection and finishing will also be covered throug
 hout the course.
SUMMARY:Intro to Woodturning
URL;VALUE=URI:https://ce.sbwi.edu/s/courseoffering/0P0Hu000000TbwJKAS
